        "timestamp": "2018-08-13 09:03:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\nIn my opinion it's counterproductive to use oparent in its current form for kotlin-based projects:\n\n1. It uses outdated plugins.\n2. It hardcodes some parts of configuration which is Java-specific.\n3. It doesn't configure Jacoco aggregate reports.\n\nFor HV-VES I'd opt for using pom with no parent for now and propose a future task to upgrade oparent so it addresses these issues.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
